    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to evaluate the empirical weight of the debate regarding the 2017 Tax Cuts and Jobs Act (TCJA), specifically comparing the \"funneling money to the top\" argument against the \"supply-side growth\" argument. The assistant abandons neutral, descriptive analysis in favor of a prescriptive and one-sided stance, repeatedly citing specific studies to dismiss the supply-side theory as non-viable.",
